### Create Transaction
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transactions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 100.00,
    "transaction_type": "WITHDRAWAL",
    "user": 1
}

###

### Get All Transactions for User
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transactions/all/?user_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Specific Transaction by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transactions/5/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update Transaction Status (e.g., mark as COMPLETED)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/transactions/11/update/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "COMPLETED"
}

###
